Interface QAFListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    QAFDataProviderIntercepter, QAFTestStepListener, QAFWebDriverCommandListener, QAFWebElementCommandListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ElementInteractor.SelectBox, ElementMetaDataListener, LiveIsExtendedWebDriver, QAFExtendedWebDriver, QAFExtendedWebElement, QAFListenerAdapter, QAFTestStepAdapter, QAFWebComponent, QAFWebDriverCommandAdapter, QAFWebElementCommandAdapter, WebDriverCommandLogger, WebForm.WebFormElement

    public interface QAFListener
    Marker interface for all QAF listeners. All QAF listeners implements this interface. Register listener using ApplicationProperties.QAF_LISTENERS
